  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">For me, the end of a year is a moment to pause and take stock. When I did that over the holidays, I took note of the projects I've worked on, what I've learned, the highs, the lows, the laughs and the harder moments, one word kept coming to me: gratitude.</p>

  <p class="mb-10 leading-relaxed">The previous 18 months began with a move from London to Northamptonshire and the beginning of a new chapter with One Group Engineering and the legend that is Ron Hartvelt. New spaces, new opportunities and a lot of learning.</p>

  <figure class="my-10">
    <img src="/images/pages/longdays-sunrisecommute.jpg" alt="Sunrise on the new commute, through wheat fields"
      class="max-w-[850px] w-full h-[500px] object-cover"
      style="object-position: center center" />
