  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">We're engineers and technicians first. The emphasis is on clear thinking, close collaboration, and getting the fundamentals right, and with a useful workshop and a very practical team. It's an environment where ideas are easy to challenge, quick to evolve, and don't stay theoretical for long.</p>

  <p class="mb-12 leading-relaxed">We're fully committed to current projects, but always open to new work, and I can guarantee you that your project will find a good home here. Get in touch.</p>

  <p class="mb-12 italic text-(--color-muted)">– Jahee Campbell-Brennan</p>

